## Executive Summary

The dynamic landing page ([landing_page.html](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/landing_page.html)) appears "messed up" compared to the static reference mockup ([index.html](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/index.html) + [styles.css](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/styles.css) + [main.js](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/main.js)) due to **fundamental architectural differences** between the two implementations.

