## Root Causes of Visual Issues

### 1. **Missing BEM CSS Architecture** ⚠️ CRITICAL

The static mockup uses a comprehensive BEM (Block Element Modifier) class system:

#### Static Mockup Classes (from [styles.css](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/styles.css)):
```css
.hero__border
.hero__border-corner
.hero__initial
.hero__initial-letter
.hero__title-word
.hero__subtitle-flourish
.hero__vessel
.hero__vessel-liquid
.compendium__card
.essence-card__illumination
.manuscript-entry__border
.alchemy-step__symbol
/* ... 200+ more classes */
```

#### Next.js Implementation:
- Uses **only Tailwind utility classes** like `px-8 py-3 bg-gold text-ink`
- Has **zero** BEM component classes
- Missing all decorative element styling

### 2. **Missing Core CSS Styles** ⚠️ CRITICAL

**Static [styles.css](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/styles.css)** includes:
- ✅ Parchment texture overlay (SVG pattern)
- ✅ Gold leaf radial gradients
- ✅ Hand-drawn border corners for hero
- ✅ Illuminated initial letter styling
- ✅ Flourish decorations
- ✅ Vessel liquid animations
- ✅ Botanical specimen styling
- ✅ Manuscript stain effects
- ✅ Mobile navigation with manuscript pages theme

**Next.js [globals.css](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/atelier-arome-web/src/app/globals.css)** includes:
- ❌ Basic reset
- ❌ CSS variables for colors
- ❌ `.btn` component class
- ❌ Nothing else

### 3. **Font Loading Issues**

#### Static Mockup:
```html
